===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[run]]-[[on]] [[sentence]]''' (''plural'' '''run-on sentences''')
#{{grammar}} an [[ungrammatical]] sentence in which two [[independent clause]]s that should be [[joined]] by either a [[semicolon]] or a [[conjunction]] or should be separate sentences are written as a single sentence, the clauses often being separated by a [[comma]].

